.section *refid='title' title
.*
.ix 'title'
.ix 'Document header' 'title'
.tag begin
.tdesc
Sets the title of the help document. The maximum length of the title is 47 characters (including spaces and
blanks) and is displayed in a single line. Other than text, the title may contain entity references and
nameit expansions.
.tno Note:
The title tag may only appear in the document header. It cannot appear on individual pages because it applies
to the document as a whole.
.tclass Document Header
.tcont Text
.tag end

